data.description: Welcome to Ocean Mile J-5!  This St. George Island Townhome at 300 Ocean Mile beach community is located on the quiet and pristine East End only steps to the white sands and water. 1 BR, 1 BA arrangement. Let's talk upgrades - entirely repainted, new master bedroom carpet and bed, remodeled bathroom, new washer & dryer, new a/c, new dishwasher, new refrigerator.  Projected GRI $58,774 DIV BY $489,000 equals 11.86% gross return!!!!!  This is a great investment.  Your return starts immediately as the unit is already booked Jan-April.
